title.rendered: AeroShield Blue Nitrile Finger Cots, box of 100 Large

content.rendered:
Finger Cots Nitrile, Powder Free Anti static 100/Box

Ideal for clean rooms, protects against contamination.

Shields fingers and material more economically and comfortably than whole hand gloves.

excerpt.rendered:
Nitrile – Latex Free and blue in colour for easy split detection
Pre – rolled for convenience, comfort and protection
Durable and long wearing for cost effectiveness
